src:
'OK boomer': millennial MP responds to heckler in New Zealand parliament – video
06 Nov 2019, 04:02 by New Zealand Parliament




Green MP Chlöe Swarbrick drops a casual 'OK boomer' in response to being heckled during her speech in a sitting of the New Zealand parliament. The captions department of NZParliament TV struggled with the millennial slang, quoting her as saying 'OK Berma'.
